  "body": "# ![Pudding Mod by TheMCBrothers](https://i.imgur.com/QPEClFO.png)\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architectury-api\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img alt=\"architectury-api\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/requires/architectury-api_vector.svg\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pudding-mod\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/curseforge_vector.svg\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pudding-mod\">\n    <img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n## Features 🍮\n- Pudding\n- Vanilla Pudding\n- Chocolate Pudding\n- Pudding Block\n- Pudding Liquid\n \n\n## Installation 🛠️\n- Find the game installation folder\n- Put the mod .jar file into the mods folder\n- If you run a server, also just put it in the server mods folder.\n \n\n## Modpacks 🎮\n- Feel free to use this in any modpack",
